IMPORTANT -- DECOMPOSE the constructor into separate typed ATOMS; never one monolith. Each atom is judged and credited INDEPENDENTLY, so a buggy step cannot sink the good ones (partial credit), and we can measure WHICH atom carries the value. The atoms and their data flow:
